<PageTitle>Home Page</PageTitle>

<h4>Hello, world!</h4>

<p>This is the demo for Blazor Dynamic Form library.</p>
<p>Open source and NuGet package coming soon.</p>
<p>This will also support popular component libraries such as Radzen, MudBlazor and MatBlazor.</p>
<br />
<br />
<h5>How does this work?</h5>
<p>This use C# attributes and reflection to dynamically create forms.</p>
<p>This is very useful for medium/large blazor websites with lots of form types/models.</p>
<p>You don't need to spend hours creating a form template for each model type!</p>
